It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Software Developer II position with Navitus Health Solutions. I bring over three years of professional experience in full-stack development, cloud-native applications, and API-first microservice architecture, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

