I have always been passionate about transparency in healthcare and making medications more affordable for people who need them, and I envision myself contributing my talent to furthering Navitus's mission of removing cost from the drug supply chain through innovative technology solutions. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

